  =E2=80=A2 send emails
  =E2=80=A2 run a small local SMTP server

  `blaze' is how we iterate on our library APIs and validate
  implementations. It=E2=80=99s experimental, but it=E2=80=99s gradually tu=
rning into a
  full email client.


